summary: Utility module for the ONNX Runtime backend that defines mappings from Optimum benchmark tasks to corresponding model types, pipelines, and ORT model classes, and provides helper routines to construct calibration and quantization configuration dictionaries for ONNX Runtime quantization workflows.
